  "time_ut": 1658134243,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0da7 \u0da1\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd9\u0da7 \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Oil from the army to come to the election for MPs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is said from the parliamentary sources that the MPs coming to the Parliament have been provided with the necessary facilities to get fuel from the army camps in their areas of residence.",
        "According to the complaints made by many MPs to the Speaker that there is no system to get fuel, facilities have been provided in this way to get fuel.",
        "Meanwhile, Acting President Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe has instructed the Chief of Security Staff, the Commanders of the three armed forces and the Inspector General of Police to provide special police protection to all the MPs coming to the Parliament to participate in the election of the new President.",
        "The government says that the government has taken steps to increase the security of all the MPs as various rebel groups are threatening them through social media.",
        "Due to the election of the new president, the security measures have been doubled in the Parliament and its surrounding areas and in addition to the police, teams of three armed forces officers have also been deployed.",
        "The main roads leading to Parliament have been completely closed for security reasons and only residents can enter those roads.",
        "Yesterday, it was seen that the special vehicles of the army were parked on the roads around the Parliament.",
        "Visitors to the Parliament have also been stopped as a security measure and the public galleries of the Parliament have also been closed.",
        "Sergeant Narendra Fernando issued a series of new instructions for journalists coming to Parliament yesterday."
      ],
